Pahami saja itu

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.880
Pihu dan Rudra harus menikah.

00:19:37.440 --> 00:19:39.200
Tapi kenapa kamu berkata begitu?

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:44.560
Lihat saya.

00:19:45.040 --> 00:19:46.560
Apakah karena Bu Pihu?

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:48.640
Beri tahu saya.
